### PRESENT OVER TIME
Calculates the presence of a field in the output result over time range.

```esql
TS k8s
| WHERE cluster == "prod" AND pod == "two"
| STATS events_received = MAX(PRESENT_OVER_TIME(events_received)) BY pod, time_bucket = TBUCKET(2 minute)
```
